title: Over 110 Gazans killed, 760 injured while waiting for food aid
description: Israeli forces killed at least 112 Palestinians and wounded another 760 in northern Gaza as they were waiting for food aid on Thursday, al Jazeera reported.

title: Iran sends Pars 1 research satellite into orbit
description: TEHRAN – Early on Thursday, Iran successfully put into orbit Pars 1 research-sensing satellite upon a Soyuz rocket from the Vostochny Cosmodrome in Russia's far eastern Amur region.

title: Six Iranians at Olympic Boxing Qualifying in Italy
description: TEHRAN - Iran has sent its top male boxers for the forthcoming 1st World Olympic Boxing Qualifying Event to Busto Arsizio, Italy.
